(17607, 'Diclac 75 mg/3ml 6 amps.', 'ديكلاك 75مجم/3 مل 6 امبولات', '27', '66', 'Diclofenac sodium', 'Mina pharm > hexal ag germany', 'Amp', 'أمبول', 'مسكن وخافض للحرارة ومضاد للالتهابات', 'Nsaid.acetic acid derivatives', '75 mg', 'Diclofenac is indicated for use in the treatment of pain and inflammation from varying sources including inflammatory conditions such as osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and ankylosing spondylitis, as well as injury-related inflammation due to surgery and physical trauma. It is often used in combination with [misoprostol] as a gastro-protective agent in patients with high risk of developing NSAID-induced ulcers.', '6223002642588', '', 1334, '2023-10-31', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
